// Variable - BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2938568701" "{HeroName}.  You have won.<em t=1>You have stolen from me the only thing that could stop you.<br><br>But I've followed you to this hiding place, {HeroName}.<em t=1>I bring you a message."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Variable - BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2175492817" "Ah...you've had a clone the whole time, I see.<em t=1>It matters not.<em t=1>I will face you both as my final act."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Variable - BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P3057652717" "Please listen to me, {HeroName}.<em t=1>You still have time to turn away from the darkness that swallows you.<em t=1>You can still change before it's too late!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Variable - BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG 
