// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Variable - BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2867850921" "I'm sorry I could not stop you, {HeroName}.<em t=1>I'm sorry I could not prevent you from drawing upon the power of that ancient well."

