// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Variable - BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3392532577" "But I am even more sorry that I could not save you from the damnation that awaits you.<em t=1>You are immortal, {HeroName}. You will still be here when everything is gone.<em t=1>And you will still exist when everything has died..."

