// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - MM_Villain_SL8-9_Task_02 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P399313999" "Desdemona is going to learn that challenging people like yourself is a <i>very</i> bad idea. However, just beating her down won't really make her learn her lesson. You'll have to go after what she holds dear: Croatoa. Burning part of the town before facing off against Desdemona will show her that when she goes after you, you're willing to go after those who can't fend for themselves.<br><br>Maybe after all of this, she will learn her lesson and stay out of your business."
// AcceptString :
"P3024422243" "Attack Croatoa!"
// SendOffString :
"P1696154235" "You'll be able to get to Croatoa through one of the Arachnos flyers. Then it's just a matter of setting up the proper bombs in order to really get things started in the town."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3076031640" "There's no time to lose, Croatoa is just <i>sitting</i> there, <i>waiting</i> to be attacked."
// TaskTitle :
"P2183437378" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Hometown Hero</color></span></scale></font>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1577502593" "You step into one of the main areas of Croatoa to see that Paragon has sent some of its police here. It seems they were anticipating an attack by you. It's too bad that there's nothing they can do to stop you now."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2426816810" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Hometown Hero</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color red><i>Morality Mission</i></color></span><br><br>It'll be a while before you know if your efforts in Croatoa were enough to make Desdemona think twice about crossing your path.<br><br>However, you <i>did</i> show those other heroes what happens when your eye is turned towards them. The fires that burned in Croatoa today will be a testament to your power for some time to come!"

